---
// Narrow cream "feeling" section that breaks the dark canvas. Editorial
// pacing — short paragraphs, a punch line, then a single CTA.
---

<section class="bg-bone text-primary py-32 sm:py-40">
  <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-0 text-center">
    <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold text-primary/60 mb-8">
      The promise
    </p>
    <h2
      class="font-h2 text-balance leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.02em] font-normal"
      style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw + 1rem, 3rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      The world is loud. The water <span
        class="italic font-h2-italic"
        style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72, 'SOFT' 50, 'WONK' 1;"
      >is not.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 font-body-lg text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.7] text-primary/80">
      <p>
        You don't need another vacation. You need a week where Tuesday feels
        like Saturday — where the only schedule is the tide, and the only
        notifications are dolphins off the bow.
      </p>
      <p>
        Eight cabins. Twelve guests. One catamaran. A captain who reads weather
        the way other people read the news, and a host whose galley produces a
        different cuisine every night without ever announcing the theme.
      </p>
      <p>
        We sail the British Virgin Islands and the Bahamas in winter, the
        Mediterranean in summer. Fourteen weeks a year. The boat goes where
        the day-charter crowds don't.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p
      class="font-serif-quote italic mt-12 text-[1.5rem] leading-[1.35] tracking-[-0.015em] text-primary"
      style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 24, 'SOFT' 50, 'WONK' 1;"
    >
      The life you've been putting off — it starts the moment the lines come off the dock.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-14">
      <a
        href="/voyages"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer bg-primary text-ink font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold px-8 py-[18px] hover:bg-accent transition-colors focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent focus-visible:outline-offset-3"
      >
        See the Voyages
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
